            "text": "{\n  \"vrff.doc.tos\": \"Read more about your personal data processing in Veriff's {{1}}\",\n  \"vrff.doc.tos.text\": \"Privacy Notice\",\n  \"vrff.doc.tos.robot.video.mandatory\": \"Your session audio and video will be recorded. Veriff uses automation to verify your identity. Read more about personal data processing and cookie usage in Veriff's {{1}}\",\n  \"vrff.doc.tos.robot.video.optional\": \"Your session audio and video may be recorded. Veriff uses automation to verify your identity. Read more about personal data processing and cookie usage in Veriff's {{1}}\",\n  \"vrff.doc.tos.robot\": \"Veriff uses automation to verify your identity. Read more about personal data processing and cookie usage in Veriff's {{1}}\",\n  \"vrff.doc.tos.hybrid\": \"Veriff conducts your identity verification on behalf of your service provider. Veriff may process your data independently for service development purposes. Read more from Veriff's {{1}}\",\n  \"vrff.web.doc.tos.robot.video.mandatory\": \"Your session audio and video will be recorded. Veriff uses automation to verify your identity. Read more about personal data processing and cookie usage in Veriff's <0></0>\",\n  \"vrff.web.doc.tos.robot.video.optional\": \"Your session audio and video may be recorded. Veriff uses automation to verify your identity. Read more about personal data processing and cookie usage in Veriff's <0></0>\",\n  \"vrff.web.doc.tos.robot\": \"Veriff uses automation to verify your identity. Read more about personal data processing and cookie usage in Veriff's <0></0>\",\n  \"vrff.doc.tos2.robot.video.mandatory\": \"Your session audio and video will be recorded.\",\n  \"vrff.doc.tos2.robot.video.optional\": \"Your session audio and video may be recorded.\",\n  \"vrff.doc.tos2.video.mandatory.no.audio\": \"Your session video will be recorded.\",\n  \"vrff.doc.tos2.video.optional.no.audio\": \"Your session video may be recorded.\",\n  \"vrff.doc.tos2.biometrics\": \"Veriff uses facial recognition to verify your identity.\",\n  \"vrff.doc.tos2.robot\": \"Veriff uses automation to verify your identity.\",\n  \"vrff.doc.tos2.hybrid\": \"Veriff conducts your identity verification on behalf of your service provider. Veriff may process your data independently for service development purposes.\",\n  \"vrff.doc.tos2.PP\": \"Read @% for details on personal data processing and cookie use.\",\n  \"vrff.doc.tos2.PP.combo\": \"Read <a>Privacy Notice</a> for details on personal data processing and cookie use.\",\n  \"vrff.doc.tos2.PP.alone\": \"Read <a>Privacy Notice</a> for details on personal data processing and cookie use.\",\n  \"vrff.doc.tos2.PP.cifas\": \"For more information about data protection, involved third parties, and data usage consequences, see <a>Privacy Notice</a>.\",\n  \"vrff.doc.tos2.terms\": \"By clicking “Let’s go!”, you agree that you have read and accept the <a>End User Terms</a>.\",\n  \"vrff.active.consent.title\": \"Click <b>Accept</b> to give consent to the statement below.\",\n  \"vrff.active.consent.description.1.listtitle\": \"The purpose of Veriff’s service is:\",\n  \"vrff.active.consent.description.1.bullet\": \"Verify or authenticate your identity\",\n  \"vrff.active.consent.description.1.bullet2\": \"Prevent fraud for our customer’s benefit\",\n  \"vrff.active.consent.description.2\": \"When you use the Veriff services, Veriff OÜ (including its affiliates, referred to here as “Veriff”, “we”, “us” and “our”) collects and processes your biometric data. We use this data, along with other data, to verify your identity, prevent fraud, and provide authentication services to our clients on an ongoing basis.\",\n  \"vrff.active.consent.description.3\": \"Veriff retains biometric data only for as long as necessary to provide these identity verification, fraud prevention, and authentication services. We do not retain biometric data for greater than three years, except as described in our Privacy Notice nor disclose your biometric data to third parties, except for our service providers that process your data on our behalf to provide the Veriff services. If you use Veriff to access a specific service, the client on whose behalf Veriff processes your data may also receive from us information about you, such as copies of the identification document and photo you provided us, and data indicating whether we were able to identify or authenticate you, but we do not disclose to clients biometric data extracted from your photos.\",\n  \"vrff.active.consent.description.4\": \"<b>By clicking “Accept”</b> you acknowledge and agree that you have read this disclosure, and that you voluntarily consent to Veriff’s and its clients’ and service providers’ collection, storage, retention, use, and disclosure of your biometric data and other information. For more information, please see our {{1}}.\",\n  \"vrff.active.consent.btn.consent\": \"Accept\",\n  \"vrff.active.consent.btn.cancel\": \"Cancel\",\n  \"vrff.trial.notice.title\": \"You’re in a test environment\",\n  \"vrff.trial.notice.description\": \"You’re about to begin an identity verification session where your personal data will be collected. The sender is currently evaluating Veriff as part of a trial. Only continue if you agree to participate in this test and share your data.\",\n  \"vrff.trial.notice.btn.consent\": \"I’m here to test\",\n  \"vrff.trial.notice.btn.cancel\": \"Exit, I'm not here to test\",\n  \"vrff.web.disabled.title\": \"Service not accessible via web\",\n  \"vrff.web.disabled.description\": \"The identity verification service is currently disabled for web access. Please contact your service provider for further instructions.\",\n  \"vrff.doc.title\": \"Please select your ID type\",\n  \"vrff.doc.instruction\": \"Which document would you like to use?\",\n  \"vrff.ID_CARD\": \"ID card\",\n  \"vrff.PASSPORT\": \"Passport\",\n  \"vrff.DRIVERS_LICENSE\": \"Driver’s license\",\n  \"vrff.RESIDENCE_PERMIT\": \"Residence permit\",\n  \"vrff.VISA\": \"Visa\",\n  \"vrff.XOTHER\": \"Other (e.g. Temporary license)\",\n  \"vrff.ID_CARD.listitem\": \"ID card\",\n  \"vrff.PASSPORT.listitem\": \"passport\",\n  \"vrff.DRIVERS_LICENSE.listitem\": \"driver’s license\",\n  \"vrff.RESIDENCE_PERMIT.listitem\": \"residence permit\",\n  \"vrff.VISA.listitem\": \"visa\",\n  \"vrff.preselect\": \"Please have your {{1}} ready\",\n  \"vrff.preselect.description\": \"Prepare your document now so we can verify you as quickly as possible.\",\n  \"vrff.preselect.VISA\": \"Please have your visa ready\",\n  \"vrff.preselect.ID_CARD\": \"Please have your ID card ready\",\n  \"vrff.preselect.PASSPORT\": \"Please have your passport ready\",\n  \"vrff.preselect.DRIVERS_LICENSE\": \"Please have your driver’s license ready\",\n  \"vrff.preselect.RESIDENCE_PERMIT\": \"Please have your residence permit ready\",\n  \"vrff.camera.warmup.friendly.title\": \"Get ready to take photos\",\n  \"vrff.camera.warmup.friendly.desc\": \"Before we begin, we just need to make sure we can access the camera and microphone. You can always change your permission settings later.\",\n  \"vrff.camera.warmup.friendly.desc.cam_only\": \"Before we begin, we just need to make sure we can access the camera. You can always change your permission settings later.\",\n  \"vrff.camera.warmup.direct.title\": \"Enable camera access\",\n  \"vrff.camera.warmup.direct.desc\": \"When prompted, please enable the camera and microphone, so we can confirm it’s really you. You can always change your permission settings later.\",\n  \"vrff.camera.warmup.direct.desc.cam_only\": \"When prompted, please enable the camera, so we can confirm it’s really you. You can always change your permission settings later.\",\n  \"vrff.hint.portrait.doc\": \"Now a selfie with your ID\",\n  \"vrff.hint.portrait.doc.title\": \"Selfie + ID\",\n  \"vrff.hint.portrait.doc.ID_CARD\": \"Take a selfie with your ID card.\",\n  \"vrff.hint.portrait.doc.ID_CARD.title\": \"Selfie with ID card\",\n  \"vrff.hint